## 1. Install packages

    npm install

---

## 2. Set up your .env.local file

    cp .env.example .env.local

Open .env.local and fill in BETTER_AUTH_SECRET with a random string.

Generate one with:

    Windows PowerShell:
    [System.Convert]::ToBase64String((1..32|ForEach{[byte](Get-Random -Max 256)}))

    Mac or Linux:
    openssl rand -base64 32

---

## 3. Set up the database

{{if .IsPrisma}}Run the migration:

    npx prisma migrate dev --name init

Open the database browser:

    npx prisma studio
{{end}}{{if .IsDrizzle}}Push the schema:

    npx drizzle-kit migrate

Open the database browser:

    npx drizzle-kit studio
{{end}}

---

## 4. Add shadcn/ui components

    npx shadcn@latest add button card input label avatar dropdown-menu badge toast separator

Browse all components at https://ui.shadcn.com

---

## 5. Start the dev server

    npm run dev

Open http://localhost:3000

