{{if .Docker}}
## Docker

    docker-compose up               Start app and database
    docker-compose up --build       Rebuild after changes
    docker-compose down             Stop everything

First time — run migrations inside the container:
{{if .IsPrisma}}    docker-compose exec app npx prisma migrate deploy
{{end}}{{if .IsDrizzle}}    docker-compose exec app npx drizzle-kit migrate
{{end}}
---

{{end}}{{if .HasGitHub}}
## GitHub OAuth setup

1. Go to https://github.com/settings/applications/new
2. Homepage URL: http://localhost:3000
3. Callback URL: http://localhost:3000/api/auth/callback/github
4. Paste Client ID into GITHUB_CLIENT_ID in .env.local
5. Paste Client Secret into GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET in .env.local
6. Restart the dev server

